WEBVTT

01:35.800 --> 01:41.250
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.360 --> 01:43.910
[Episode 36]

01:44.200 --> 01:47.940
[Three days later]

01:54.860 --> 01:57.110
[Jingque Pavilion]

01:56.229 --> 01:57.430
So many people today.

01:57.590 --> 01:58.590
Quite boisterous.

01:58.590 --> 01:59.200
Yes.

02:01.000 --> 02:01.760
Sister,

02:01.880 --> 02:03.070
you can't stand being apart

02:03.070 --> 02:04.710
from the marquis for even one second.

02:04.710 --> 02:06.840
Why did you have to come
and join the crowd?

02:06.840 --> 02:08.870
He showed me support
when I entered the Capital.

02:08.870 --> 02:10.430
Now that he's coming back in triumph,

02:10.430 --> 02:12.560
of course I must be here to cheer him on.

02:14.960 --> 02:17.150
Song Yan of the Ministry of Rites'
Department of Internal Affairs

02:17.150 --> 02:19.579
was appointed to uphold ritual practice
and educate the people,

02:19.579 --> 02:21.329
yet he failed to fulfill his duties

02:21.329 --> 02:23.190
and was derelict in his responsibilities.

02:23.190 --> 02:24.430
He is hereby dismissed from office

02:24.430 --> 02:25.960
and sent back to his place of origin.

02:25.960 --> 02:28.820
He shall not be trusted
with an official post again.

02:30.560 --> 02:31.360
Here he comes!

02:31.140 --> 02:34.370
[Yong'an Gate]

02:31.910 --> 02:34.170
-Here comes the marquis!
-Here he comes!

02:34.480 --> 02:37.770
[Guo's Restaurant]

02:37.710 --> 02:39.440
There he is. Sister, come look!

02:40.350 --> 02:41.270
He's getting close!

02:41.270 --> 02:42.900
Marquis of Wu'an!

02:42.980 --> 02:44.340
Marquis of Wu'an!

02:44.350 --> 02:48.290
♪ The world is vast ♪

02:44.410 --> 02:46.540
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

02:47.350 --> 02:50.850
[Yong'an Gate]

02:49.740 --> 02:55.730
♪ The storm is rising ♪

02:57.310 --> 03:01.400
♪ Day and night ♪

03:03.140 --> 03:06.590
♪ We strive to save the world ♪

03:07.270 --> 03:08.610
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

03:08.610 --> 03:10.500
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

03:10.500 --> 03:14.980
♪ All people ♪

03:15.890 --> 03:21.320
♪ Are part of the past ♪

03:19.870 --> 03:21.020
Marquis of Wu'an!

03:23.550 --> 03:28.329
♪ What's the date today? ♪

03:28.860 --> 03:35.700
♪ How lamentable ♪

03:32.079 --> 03:33.410
Why don't you come over?

03:34.960 --> 03:36.790
What's there to see? I'm not going there.

03:36.680 --> 03:41.630
♪ What's the date today? ♪

03:39.650 --> 03:45.500
[Yong'an Gate]

03:39.670 --> 03:41.910
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

03:42.440 --> 03:48.990
♪ How lamentable ♪

03:43.360 --> 03:45.220
Eyes over here, Marquis of Wu'an!

03:45.560 --> 03:47.780
Marquis of Wu'an! Marquis of Wu'an!

03:48.000 --> 03:51.030
-Look at me!
-Please look at me, Marquis of Wu'an!

03:51.030 --> 03:52.710
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

03:52.710 --> 03:54.310
Look at me, Marquis of Wu'an!

03:56.990 --> 03:59.100
[Xie]

04:03.440 --> 04:06.230
[Xie]

04:34.750 --> 04:35.430
Halt!

04:38.240 --> 04:38.920
Sister,

04:39.360 --> 04:41.560
why don't you throw a handkerchief too?

04:42.430 --> 04:43.490
I didn't bring any.

04:43.510 --> 04:44.390
Just throw one.

04:45.040 --> 04:46.570
Anyone has a handkerchief?

04:46.920 --> 04:47.920
Does anyone have a handkerchief?

04:47.920 --> 04:48.920
Did you bring any?

04:49.070 --> 04:51.470
What's the fun in throwing handkerchiefs?

04:51.510 --> 04:52.040
Watch me.

04:52.190 --> 04:54.050
I'll show you what should be done.

04:59.409 --> 05:01.410
I'm going to knock you out with this.

05:03.630 --> 05:05.360
What do you think you're doing?

05:05.390 --> 05:05.950
I...

05:05.950 --> 05:07.500
Go on and say it. What?

05:07.340 --> 05:09.540
[Guo's Restaurant]

05:42.880 --> 05:45.850
[Xu's Restaurant]

05:51.560 --> 05:53.740
Who threw that hair ribbon?

05:54.480 --> 05:56.950
Is the Marquis of Wu'an
in love with someone?

05:58.240 --> 05:58.870
Hyah!

05:59.780 --> 06:04.540
[Marquis of Wu'an]

06:01.360 --> 06:03.270
So many girls threw handkerchiefs
along the way,

06:03.270 --> 06:04.870
yet the marquis didn't spare
a glance at them.

06:04.870 --> 06:08.070
Which noble family's daughter
the marquis has his eye on?

06:09.800 --> 06:11.920
Isn't that the Flower-Crowned General?

06:11.920 --> 06:13.320
It really is General Fan!

06:14.950 --> 06:16.910
Marquis of Wu'an is into her?

06:16.740 --> 06:20.890
[Jingque Pavilion]

06:23.120 --> 06:25.870
General Fan is truly a heroine
who can rival any man.

06:25.870 --> 06:27.870
No wonder the Marquis of Wu'an
only likes her.

06:27.870 --> 06:28.360
So what?

06:28.360 --> 06:29.940
The marquis is a battle-hardened warrior

06:29.940 --> 06:32.040
-who won't be trapped by romantic trifles!
-That's right!

06:32.040 --> 06:33.310
That pig butcher you're fans of

06:33.310 --> 06:34.560
are not worthy of the marquis at all!

06:34.560 --> 06:35.790
Not worthy of him at all!

06:35.630 --> 06:41.710
[Li's Wine House]

06:35.820 --> 06:37.600
The Flower-Crowned General
is a skillful fighter.

06:37.600 --> 06:39.680
She captured Lord Changxin
and won distinction in battle many times.

06:39.680 --> 06:41.830
She will by no means
deign to marry the marquis!

06:41.830 --> 06:43.390
Stop flattering the marquis!

06:43.390 --> 06:44.040
That's right!

06:44.040 --> 06:45.430
Stop flattering the marquis!

06:45.430 --> 06:47.430
The marquis, our hero,
is mighty and extraordinary.

06:47.430 --> 06:49.750
He will never settle for a pig butcher
like the one you admire!

06:49.750 --> 06:51.070
Right. What's so great about

06:51.070 --> 06:53.680
-that lowly pig butcher?
-The general contributed a lot in battle.

06:53.680 --> 06:55.480
She won't marry that brute you call hero!

06:55.480 --> 06:57.280
What brute? Stop spewing filth!

06:59.430 --> 07:00.360
Quiet down!

07:00.600 --> 07:01.870
All we want is just a good show

07:01.870 --> 07:03.310
about a hero and a beauty.

07:03.310 --> 07:04.870
Can't you stop shouting and yelling?

07:04.870 --> 07:05.800
Exactly.

07:07.350 --> 07:08.610
-Look at that!
-I know!

07:09.860 --> 07:11.250
You're going too fast.

07:12.170 --> 07:14.300
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

07:15.870 --> 07:17.350
Look here!

07:17.180 --> 07:20.140
[Xie]

07:21.010 --> 07:23.140
-Look here, Marquis of Wu'an!
-Here!

07:28.740 --> 07:30.080
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

07:30.080 --> 07:31.630
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

07:31.630 --> 07:33.730
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

07:33.730 --> 07:35.530
Look at me please!

07:53.980 --> 07:55.580
The heavens are unfair.

08:06.700 --> 08:11.210
[Xie's Mausoleum]

08:59.730 --> 09:01.300
As I am getting old,

09:02.750 --> 09:04.150
my memory is failing too.

09:04.790 --> 09:05.650
I can't believe

09:06.150 --> 09:09.410
I forgot to bring
your favorite osmanthus cake here today.

09:27.630 --> 09:30.030
You visit this place
every year on this day.

09:30.080 --> 09:31.960
Do you just hate to see my parents

09:32.240 --> 09:33.750
rest in peace

09:34.390 --> 09:36.650
so you come here to upset them
once a year?

09:40.120 --> 09:42.390
After skulking around for days,

09:43.030 --> 09:45.000
you finally decided to show up.

09:50.510 --> 09:53.440
Today is the anniversary
of your mother's death.

09:54.240 --> 09:57.150
Let's save the fight and feud
for another day.

10:06.790 --> 10:08.540
Anything can wait

10:08.910 --> 10:12.400
till the ritual to pay respects
to your parents is finished.

10:13.960 --> 10:14.670
Come.

10:33.200 --> 10:37.130
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

10:40.740 --> 10:44.450
[Memorial Tablets for Xie's Ancestors]

10:57.170 --> 11:00.120
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

11:29.080 --> 11:36.710
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

11:30.030 --> 11:32.490
You've dismissed all the Suicide Warriors.

11:32.840 --> 11:33.840
Aren't you afraid

11:34.510 --> 11:37.570
that I'll make you pay blood for blood,
Prime Minister?

11:38.600 --> 11:41.670
Your mother is watching right here.

11:42.440 --> 11:44.600
Why would I put you in a tough spot

11:45.440 --> 11:46.870
and disturb her peace?

11:49.870 --> 11:51.030
Prime Minister Wei,

11:52.200 --> 11:55.530
today, you finally know to
show care for your little sister.

11:57.510 --> 11:58.710
Seventeen years ago,

11:59.270 --> 12:02.000
you returned to the Capital
in the middle of deploying troops.

12:02.000 --> 12:03.260
Did it ever occur to you

12:04.700 --> 12:06.100
that my father and mother

12:06.630 --> 12:09.480
would lose their lives
for your rash decision?

12:13.910 --> 12:15.770
Let me tell you this one more time:

12:16.510 --> 12:17.790
seventeen years ago,

12:18.720 --> 12:22.320
I came back to the Capital
to quell a rebellion by imperial order.

12:22.630 --> 12:23.390
Was that so?

12:25.390 --> 12:28.850
Then before my parents' memorial tablets,
do you dare to swear

12:29.870 --> 12:31.070
a solemn oath on that?

12:34.390 --> 12:36.600
Fine. Now that we've gone this far,

12:37.390 --> 12:38.200
today,

12:38.550 --> 12:41.410
I might as well share
a few heartfelt words with you.

12:44.790 --> 12:46.360
I raised you up

12:47.170 --> 12:48.870
only with the purpose of enabling you

12:48.870 --> 12:51.400
to shape a future
for the Xie and Wei families,

12:51.960 --> 12:58.980
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

12:52.050 --> 12:53.580
to bring glory to our clans,

12:54.550 --> 12:58.840
and to guard the peace of Great Yin.

12:59.440 --> 13:00.240
That is why

13:00.790 --> 13:02.840
I spared no effort in nurturing you.

13:02.840 --> 13:03.720
Nurturing?

13:05.440 --> 13:07.960
You were simply forging a handy blade.

13:10.000 --> 13:11.660
It just never came to your mind

13:12.030 --> 13:13.160
that this very blade

13:14.150 --> 13:16.550
would eventually be directed at yourself.

13:18.720 --> 13:19.670
And you are...

13:20.870 --> 13:23.240
the one sullying the clans' reputation

13:23.440 --> 13:25.640
and disrupting the peace of the nation.

13:28.150 --> 13:30.600
You're acting disloyally and unfilially
for being bewitched

13:30.600 --> 13:32.200
by the daughter of our enemy.

13:32.390 --> 13:35.890
Who are you to talk about the greater good
of family and country to me?

13:35.890 --> 13:39.320
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

13:36.030 --> 13:39.270
Today, right before your parents,
I command you

13:39.270 --> 13:41.120
to make a clean break and sever all ties

13:41.120 --> 13:41.720
with Fan Changyu!

13:41.720 --> 13:43.050
What gives you the right

13:43.630 --> 13:45.380
to say all that to me at this very place?

13:45.380 --> 13:46.980
I spent 17 years raising you.

13:47.670 --> 13:49.270
Does it not give me the right?

13:52.320 --> 13:52.810
Do you...

13:52.810 --> 13:53.620
admit it

13:54.550 --> 13:55.750
or not?

13:59.750 --> 14:00.610
Yes, I admit it.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.960
As your uncle,

14:07.390 --> 14:10.000
I am to exercise
the authority of your parents.

14:10.630 --> 14:11.440
Today,

14:12.000 --> 14:14.600
I shall punish you
according to the family rules.

14:14.600 --> 14:15.390
Tell him

14:15.870 --> 14:17.130
about the punishment!

14:18.150 --> 14:19.450
The family rules dictate

14:19.450 --> 14:20.510
that anyone disloyal and unfilial

14:20.510 --> 14:22.170
shall receive 108 whippings.

14:24.730 --> 14:25.410
Fine.

14:27.750 --> 14:29.170
I will willingly take

14:29.360 --> 14:30.890
all those whippings today.

14:31.750 --> 14:33.950
Consider it my way to return your favor.

14:36.020 --> 14:37.400
From today on,

14:38.320 --> 14:40.120
stop saying disgusting words

14:40.840 --> 14:43.240
like how I'm indebted to you
for raising me.

14:52.550 --> 14:53.150
Do it now!

15:06.800 --> 15:08.330
Our illustrious ancestors

15:09.030 --> 15:10.830
left a glorious name in history.

15:11.240 --> 15:13.040
All descendants are instructed

15:13.910 --> 15:15.570
to follow the righteous path.

15:41.730 --> 15:44.260
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

15:43.360 --> 15:44.320
Thirty-five.

15:47.150 --> 15:47.910
Thirty-six.

15:51.480 --> 15:52.510
Thirty-seven.

15:54.150 --> 15:55.120
Thirty-eight.

15:56.950 --> 15:57.910
Thirty-nine.

16:00.320 --> 16:01.150
Forty.

16:01.830 --> 16:07.040
[Family Creed]

16:07.090 --> 16:11.560
[Foster Family Unity and Harmony]

16:19.600 --> 16:20.610
Ninety-nine.

16:38.020 --> 16:39.220
One hundred and four.

16:44.790 --> 16:45.920
One hundred and six.

16:48.510 --> 16:49.770
One hundred and seven.

16:53.480 --> 16:54.770
One hundred and eight!

18:05.110 --> 18:06.000
Yan Zheng.

18:09.640 --> 18:10.480
Yan Zheng.

18:25.440 --> 18:26.700
You shouldn't be here.

18:27.840 --> 18:28.970
I really shouldn't.

18:30.360 --> 18:31.420
But what about you?

18:33.470 --> 18:35.530
You knew Wei Yan was at the mausoleum.

18:36.550 --> 18:38.080
why did you come here alone?

18:38.550 --> 18:40.680
Why were you punished with whippings?

18:42.550 --> 18:45.160
General Fan, it's a breach of etiquette

18:45.480 --> 18:47.810
for you to barge into the Xie's mausoleum.

18:48.750 --> 18:50.150
I am not only General Fan,

18:52.310 --> 18:53.770
but also the Marchioness.

18:54.310 --> 18:55.370
Why can't I be here?

18:55.550 --> 18:58.160
A marriage is not valid
without parental consent

18:58.160 --> 18:59.960
and a matchmaker's involvment.

19:00.110 --> 19:01.160
On top of that,

19:01.720 --> 19:04.120
have there been proper betrothal rituals?

19:05.350 --> 19:07.410
As for him marrying into your family,

19:07.440 --> 19:09.240
even the name he gave you is fake.

19:09.510 --> 19:11.920
How can this marriage be taken for real?

19:11.920 --> 19:13.880
I've had all the 108 whippings.

19:14.920 --> 19:17.920
You're in no position to decide for me.

19:21.510 --> 19:24.170
A marriage certificate
is just a piece of paper.

19:24.200 --> 19:25.660
Only when I acknowledge it

19:26.920 --> 19:28.380
will it become effective.

19:29.880 --> 19:30.720
Let's go home.

19:30.960 --> 19:31.640
Not now.

19:38.510 --> 19:39.510
Get on your knees.

19:43.460 --> 19:46.040
[Memorial Tablets for Xie's Ancestors]

19:56.880 --> 19:58.680
Father, Mother, please listen.

19:59.310 --> 20:00.640
This lady, Fan Changyu,

20:00.920 --> 20:02.050
is from Lin'an Town.

20:04.320 --> 20:06.320
When my life was hanging by a thread,

20:08.900 --> 20:10.170
she saved me.

20:12.890 --> 20:14.660
When I was in sheer despair,

20:16.440 --> 20:17.600
she gave me her love.

20:18.460 --> 20:20.350
During my ten-odd years
on the battlefield,

20:19.440 --> 20:23.040
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

20:22.510 --> 20:24.440
I never felt like I was truly alive.

20:23.860 --> 20:26.210
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

20:26.740 --> 20:30.120
♪ For a chance encounter ♪

20:26.830 --> 20:27.760
I didn't realize

20:31.290 --> 20:34.990
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

20:32.070 --> 20:34.270
my life was worth living until I met her.

20:35.270 --> 20:37.590
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

20:37.870 --> 20:41.490
♪ Just for a glance ♪

20:41.680 --> 20:42.440
♪ In this life ♪

20:42.460 --> 20:45.150
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

20:45.170 --> 20:46.780
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

20:47.110 --> 20:47.960
♪ On this journey ♪

20:47.990 --> 20:50.970
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

20:50.990 --> 20:52.970
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

20:52.990 --> 20:53.840
♪ After we part ♪

20:53.860 --> 20:56.850
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

20:56.880 --> 20:59.190
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

20:59.210 --> 21:03.720
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

21:04.170 --> 21:07.570
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

21:05.270 --> 21:08.200
I now respectfully announce to you,
my departed parents,

21:08.200 --> 21:09.060
that this woman

21:10.240 --> 21:11.640
is the love of my life.

21:12.350 --> 21:13.680
I will never betray her,

21:15.110 --> 21:16.570
not until death do us part.

21:27.370 --> 21:28.130
♪ In this life ♪

21:28.150 --> 21:30.740
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

21:30.760 --> 21:32.310
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

21:32.800 --> 21:33.660
♪ On this journey ♪

21:33.690 --> 21:36.530
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

21:36.560 --> 21:38.540
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

21:38.570 --> 21:39.390
♪ After we part ♪

21:39.410 --> 21:42.330
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

21:42.350 --> 21:44.650
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

21:42.650 --> 21:44.320
I will never betray you,

21:44.670 --> 21:49.230
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

21:45.830 --> 21:48.000
not until death do us part.

21:50.160 --> 21:56.690
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

21:59.240 --> 22:00.170
Prime Minister.

22:03.790 --> 22:04.550
Zheng!

22:06.640 --> 22:07.310
Zheng!

22:07.880 --> 22:08.590
Zheng.

22:10.750 --> 22:11.950
What happened to you?

22:11.960 --> 22:13.330
Why are you so badly hurt?

22:13.330 --> 22:14.510
I'm fine, Aunt.

22:17.830 --> 22:19.000
This is Fan Changyu,

22:20.350 --> 22:21.310
my wife.

22:29.960 --> 22:30.640
Aunt.

22:31.380 --> 22:32.840
Flower-Crowned General,

22:33.070 --> 22:35.800
I have long heard of
your formidable reputation.

22:37.400 --> 22:39.200
When my life was in grave danger,

22:40.280 --> 22:41.540
it was she who saved me.

22:45.070 --> 22:46.470
We have pledged our lives

22:46.880 --> 22:48.410
to each other and committed

22:49.070 --> 22:50.670
to lifelong companionship.

22:53.390 --> 22:54.480
Now, Changyu,

22:54.960 --> 22:57.160
take Zheng away for medical treatment.

22:57.400 --> 22:58.770
Zheng, get up.

23:20.790 --> 23:22.110
It is cold and damp.

23:22.400 --> 23:24.160
What brings you here, my love?

23:25.000 --> 23:27.880
I noticed that you had prepared
osmanthus cake but forgot to take it

23:27.880 --> 23:28.790
with you.

23:29.000 --> 23:31.440
So I hurriedly brought it here to you.

23:33.750 --> 23:37.070
Zheng's mother loved osmanthus cake.

23:37.330 --> 23:39.120
In memory of her, you would

23:39.220 --> 23:41.480
offer it to her spirit tablet every year.

23:42.000 --> 23:44.060
This year is no exception, of course.

23:50.130 --> 23:50.860
Here you are.

24:00.960 --> 24:02.990
What an exquisite box.

24:03.200 --> 24:05.880
Was it made by a master craftsman?

24:08.100 --> 24:10.280
I must have some more cake every day

24:10.510 --> 24:11.770
so the effort you put in

24:12.350 --> 24:15.350
won't be wasted—
your hand was hurt for making the box.

24:23.110 --> 24:24.310
Osmanthus cake is too sweet

24:24.310 --> 24:25.440
to be taken too much.

24:25.590 --> 24:26.310
Got it.

24:49.540 --> 24:51.340
They make such a perfect couple.

24:51.510 --> 24:54.830
Zheng's parents, may they rest in peace,

24:55.680 --> 24:57.580
would surely be happy about it.

25:07.880 --> 25:09.350
Fifteen, twenty, ten!

25:10.480 --> 25:12.400
-Fifteen, twenty, twenty!
-Fifteen, twenty, ten!

25:12.400 --> 25:12.930
Drink up.

25:14.640 --> 25:17.070
What kind of stupid game is this
from your hometown?

25:17.070 --> 25:18.600
I've been losing all night.

25:21.240 --> 25:22.100
One more round.

25:22.350 --> 25:24.480
-Fifteen, twenty, twenty!
-Fifteen, twenty, ten!

25:24.480 --> 25:26.070
Fifteen, twenty, ten!

25:26.960 --> 25:27.880
Drink up.

25:30.160 --> 25:30.790
Quick!

25:32.000 --> 25:32.550
Master.

25:34.640 --> 25:35.920
What's the matter? Speak up.

25:35.920 --> 25:37.320
No outsiders are around.

25:38.640 --> 25:39.970
Here's a letter for you.

25:46.590 --> 25:49.720
I knew Xie Zheng wouldn't quit
his quest for the truth.

25:51.590 --> 25:53.720
To hell with that uncle-nephew bond.

25:56.880 --> 25:58.610
Seems like it's time to strike.

26:02.030 --> 26:03.070
Come with me.

26:04.030 --> 26:06.090
What's there to do this late at night?

26:07.960 --> 26:10.590
I have prepared a surprise for you.

26:18.350 --> 26:20.680
I've got you a magnificent robe and crown.

26:21.400 --> 26:22.400
What do you think?

26:43.510 --> 26:44.840
Are you out of your mind?

26:45.530 --> 26:47.080
This is an empress's crown.

26:48.960 --> 26:50.360
I want you to be my empress

26:50.830 --> 26:52.430
and the mother to the nation.

26:52.510 --> 26:53.840
You will stand by my side

26:54.510 --> 26:56.110
and rule the country with me.

27:01.390 --> 27:03.120
So what if I become the Empress?

27:03.790 --> 27:06.310
You're only looking for someone
to share a bed with you,

27:06.310 --> 27:09.710
so you won't be alone
when your beautiful dreams all shatter.

27:12.110 --> 27:12.830
What?

27:14.790 --> 27:15.920
Do you not like them?

27:17.400 --> 27:18.440
At this point,

27:19.110 --> 27:20.170
does it even matter

27:20.720 --> 27:22.180
whether I like them or not?

27:23.860 --> 27:25.340
You told me not to kill,

27:25.860 --> 27:26.830
so I stopped.

27:27.590 --> 27:28.920
I have also promised you

27:29.310 --> 27:31.240
not to hurt that little brat again.

27:32.310 --> 27:33.810
What do I have to do

27:34.750 --> 27:36.680
for you to willingly be my empress?

27:58.550 --> 27:59.680
Kneel before me,

28:00.350 --> 28:01.160
and beg me.

28:07.550 --> 28:09.350
You're asking me to kneel to you?

28:12.590 --> 28:14.480
I am the ruler of all.

28:17.350 --> 28:18.270
What now?

28:19.160 --> 28:20.160
Is that a refusal?

28:49.770 --> 28:50.890
I beg you...

28:51.890 --> 28:53.340
to be my empress.

29:04.220 --> 29:06.750
I look forward to the day
I become the Empress.

29:09.780 --> 29:11.070
It won't take long.

30:18.580 --> 30:19.780
Stop messing around.

30:20.730 --> 30:22.330
Give me back the Tiger Tally.

30:50.940 --> 30:55.970
[Xie's Mansion]

31:01.480 --> 31:01.960
My Lord!

31:05.640 --> 31:06.200
My Lord.

31:07.750 --> 31:09.030
My Lady, what happened?

31:09.030 --> 31:09.960
Bring him to his room.

31:09.960 --> 31:10.830
Don't disclose a word.

31:10.830 --> 31:11.400
Yes.

31:21.070 --> 31:23.720
My Lady, would you like to take a rest?

31:24.000 --> 31:25.790
I will attend to His Lordship.

31:26.200 --> 31:26.880
Let me do it.

31:27.310 --> 31:28.510
You may all leave now.

31:29.400 --> 31:30.530
Unless it is urgent,

31:30.590 --> 31:31.590
do not disturb us.

31:31.680 --> 31:32.270
Yes.

31:48.000 --> 31:49.110
Changyu...

31:52.680 --> 31:55.120
After taking those 108 whippings,

31:57.320 --> 31:59.410
now I can rightfully wed you

32:01.640 --> 32:04.680
following the complete marriage rituals.

32:21.110 --> 32:23.110
It turns out you had already decided

32:24.270 --> 32:26.220
to atone for your sins this way.

32:29.680 --> 32:30.880
Changyu,

32:32.830 --> 32:34.590
will you let me take you...

32:36.920 --> 32:37.830
as my wife?

32:56.450 --> 32:57.830
No need for that.

32:58.790 --> 33:01.110
You have long belonged to me already.

33:37.790 --> 33:38.960
Mother Consort,

33:40.440 --> 33:41.350
don't...

33:42.880 --> 33:43.810
Mother Consort,

33:45.770 --> 33:46.960
let me die.

34:19.150 --> 34:21.920
This is enough to last you a lifetime.

34:22.480 --> 34:23.920
Deliver this package safely

34:23.920 --> 34:25.600
to the General's Mansion.

34:26.000 --> 34:27.330
Then leave the Capital.

34:27.440 --> 34:28.280
Go as far away as you can.

34:28.280 --> 34:29.540
Do not come back again.

34:31.230 --> 34:33.400
My Lady, won't you leave with me?

34:35.440 --> 34:37.550
Qi Min's men have this place
under close watch.

34:37.550 --> 34:38.480
I cannot escape.

34:39.360 --> 34:40.190
Once I leave,

34:40.960 --> 34:42.560
more people here will die.

34:47.320 --> 34:48.000
Off you go.

34:57.360 --> 34:57.920
Go.

35:53.170 --> 35:54.060
You're awake?

35:57.360 --> 35:58.110
Careful.

36:05.360 --> 36:06.420
Thank you...

36:07.920 --> 36:09.250
for keeping me company.

36:14.110 --> 36:16.190
You took many whippings for me.

36:17.880 --> 36:19.550
How could I leave you?

36:23.320 --> 36:24.710
I always thought

36:25.280 --> 36:26.760
Wei Yan hated me

36:27.480 --> 36:29.440
because my mother took the opportunity

36:29.440 --> 36:31.300
to hang herself while I was eating

36:31.400 --> 36:33.730
that plate of osmanthus cake out of greed.

36:35.030 --> 36:37.630
I also hated myself for that ever since.

36:39.170 --> 36:42.370
Later, though I conquered Jinzhou
to complete my revenge

36:44.150 --> 36:45.950
and became the Marquis of Wu'an,

36:46.630 --> 36:48.030
I could dream of nothing

36:48.920 --> 36:51.120
but that revolting scent of osmanthus

36:51.800 --> 36:54.930
and the hem of my mother's dress
dangling under the beam.

36:59.670 --> 37:01.000
I am still that child...

37:01.440 --> 37:02.550
who loves to cry.

37:04.190 --> 37:05.590
I've never changed a bit.

37:14.030 --> 37:15.280
Now you have me.

37:17.210 --> 37:18.330
I can protect you.

37:25.920 --> 37:26.880
You know what?

37:27.280 --> 37:29.890
When you left Lin'an to look for me

37:30.110 --> 37:31.910
and showed up covered in wounds,

37:32.840 --> 37:34.490
I thought to myself,

37:35.110 --> 37:36.910
"what's the point of vengeance?

37:36.920 --> 37:37.920
I'm done with it."

37:39.630 --> 37:41.160
I didn't want to see you cry.

37:43.800 --> 37:44.740
But then,

37:45.590 --> 37:47.520
I remembered my family name "Xie,"

37:49.760 --> 37:51.690
and that my father was Xie Linshan.

37:52.320 --> 37:54.190
I can hardly recall his face,

37:57.060 --> 37:58.420
yet the barely

38:00.280 --> 38:01.680
stitched-up chest of his

38:02.500 --> 38:04.690
after he was disemboweled

38:05.630 --> 38:07.590
and the 67 arrow-shaped wounds on his body

38:07.590 --> 38:09.550
are still vivid in my mind.

38:11.480 --> 38:12.360
Yan Zheng,

38:14.360 --> 38:15.880
I've never blamed you.

38:17.850 --> 38:19.280
Wei Yan is your uncle,

38:19.880 --> 38:22.010
who raised you for more than ten years.

38:22.880 --> 38:25.180
You've paid him the debt of gratitude now.

38:25.180 --> 38:26.710
It is time you took revenge.

38:27.070 --> 38:28.870
It's wrong to torture ourselves

38:29.760 --> 38:31.360
over the mistakes of others.

38:44.280 --> 38:44.760
I got it.

38:48.440 --> 38:49.480
It is time.

38:50.710 --> 38:52.400
When the royal banquet is held
three days later,

38:52.400 --> 38:54.060
I will enter the palace myself

38:54.550 --> 38:57.480
and bring out the maids
who bore witness to the truth.

38:57.630 --> 38:58.440
I'll help you.

39:02.880 --> 39:03.440
Come in.

39:06.440 --> 39:08.170
Your Lordship, Your Ladyship.

39:08.670 --> 39:10.920
The falcon brought back a chess record
from the palace.

39:10.920 --> 39:12.320
Mr. Gongsun cracked it

39:12.440 --> 39:14.570
and wrote this note for Your Lordship.

39:22.230 --> 39:22.920
What is it?

39:26.730 --> 39:29.060
Wei Yan had an affair
with a royal consort.

39:31.970 --> 39:35.400
[Wisdom and Integrity]

39:43.920 --> 39:44.710
This woman

39:45.510 --> 39:46.920
is the love of my life.

39:47.630 --> 39:48.890
I'll never betray her,

39:49.510 --> 39:50.970
not until death do us part.

39:52.400 --> 39:53.760
To Yan, my dearest:

39:54.030 --> 39:55.890
I hope this letter finds you well.

39:57.320 --> 39:59.630
I have missed you so much since we parted.

39:59.920 --> 40:01.670
Every time I adorn myself
before the mirror,

40:01.670 --> 40:03.200
put on the clothes you like,

40:04.800 --> 40:06.480
and watch the blooms and butterflies
in the garden,

40:06.480 --> 40:09.080
I'm sad that no one is there
to share my joy with.

40:09.760 --> 40:10.800
The elders at home

40:10.800 --> 40:12.600
have consented to our marriage.

40:12.880 --> 40:14.400
All auspicious signs have gathered.

40:14.400 --> 40:15.780
Our two families rejoice.

40:15.160 --> 40:18.890
[Consort Virtue, Qi Rongyin]

40:16.000 --> 40:17.030
The six betrothal rites
have been duly performed,

40:17.030 --> 40:19.190
and all the ceremonial gifts are ready.

40:19.190 --> 40:21.720
Now, everything has been
properly arranged.

40:21.840 --> 40:23.300
Your company is all I need.

40:24.510 --> 40:25.920
I'll never betray you,

40:26.510 --> 40:27.970
not until death do us part.

40:39.110 --> 40:40.440
To Yan, my dearest:

40:41.840 --> 40:44.590
I hope you can feel my presence
through these words.

40:44.590 --> 40:46.720
An imperial decree arrived suddenly,

40:46.840 --> 40:48.770
summoning me into the royal harem.

40:49.440 --> 40:51.240
Bound by the Emperor's command,

40:51.630 --> 40:53.070
I have no other choice.

40:54.030 --> 40:56.000
As I savor the letters you wrote me,

40:56.630 --> 40:58.230
I feel deep affection.

40:58.670 --> 41:00.510
Every word is engraved in my heart,

41:00.510 --> 41:02.170
as if it is whispered in my ear.

41:02.590 --> 41:05.250
In the old days,
you would pin flowers in my hair.

41:05.710 --> 41:07.370
The fragrance still lingers,

41:07.760 --> 41:09.960
as if all that just happened yesterday.

41:10.430 --> 41:12.290
The greatest regret in this world

41:12.920 --> 41:15.440
is for two people in love to be separated.

41:16.320 --> 41:18.850
From now on,
I will be trapped in a golden cage,

41:19.320 --> 41:22.000
but my heart will roam with the clouds.

41:23.550 --> 41:25.550
If you see a wild goose flying south,

41:26.670 --> 41:28.800
consider it a loving message from me.

41:29.960 --> 41:30.760
From Rongyin,

41:31.710 --> 41:33.670
in tears before departure.

41:35.390 --> 41:38.560
[Li's Mansion]

42:09.450 --> 42:10.250
Grandfather.

42:11.800 --> 42:12.800
Guards,

42:13.510 --> 42:15.840
take down my dear brother.

42:19.800 --> 42:21.130
What do you mean by this?

42:21.840 --> 42:23.070
You will understand

42:23.670 --> 42:25.110
after the royal banquet.

42:34.590 --> 42:36.310
So you've been feigning illness,
Grandfather.

42:36.310 --> 42:37.650
Wenkan,

42:38.800 --> 42:41.880
do you know how you failed?

42:42.880 --> 42:45.840
He who is to achieve great things
must be decisive

42:45.840 --> 42:48.480
and remain composed
when emotions are involved.

42:48.480 --> 42:50.070
Your temperament determines

42:50.070 --> 42:52.670
that you will fail
in every great undertaking.

42:54.340 --> 42:56.000
I act for the best of the family

42:56.230 --> 42:57.920
and the country,
while you for selfish gain.

42:57.920 --> 43:00.320
I'm not fated to become
an unscrupulous man

43:00.710 --> 43:02.040
like you, Grandfather.

43:02.150 --> 43:03.370
You're such a fool!

43:04.090 --> 43:06.160
What has years of loyalty brought

43:06.550 --> 43:07.760
us the Li family?

43:07.920 --> 43:09.580
What have we gained in return?

43:09.880 --> 43:11.070
We have reached

43:11.070 --> 43:13.400
a point of no turning back.

43:13.670 --> 43:16.930
We must ensure
the Emperor's grandson ascends the throne.

43:17.280 --> 43:19.000
Even if he can't be a benevolent ruler,

43:19.000 --> 43:21.960
we've embarked on a journey
we can't turn back from.

43:23.550 --> 43:24.280
Wenkan,

43:25.110 --> 43:27.870
there are thousands in our Li clan.

43:27.960 --> 43:30.110
You must stop confusing friends with foes

43:30.110 --> 43:31.430
and siding with outsiders,

43:31.430 --> 43:34.170
or the entire Li clan will be doomed,

43:34.550 --> 43:37.710
and the foundations of Great Yin
will be shaken.

43:41.510 --> 43:44.320
To the victor belongs the spoils—
it's a rule since the ancient times.

43:44.320 --> 43:45.670
One won't devote his life

43:45.670 --> 43:48.360
to his country
unless personal interest is involved.

43:48.360 --> 43:49.280
Oh, you...

43:49.630 --> 43:50.630
All those studies

43:51.110 --> 43:53.000
have made you a stubborn fool.

43:54.600 --> 43:56.110
The Eldest Young Master must not leave

43:56.110 --> 43:58.000
the premises
unless I order otherwise.

43:58.000 --> 43:58.710
-Yes!
-Yes!
